::Spears::

She sighed and smiled. "I trust you." She flet him rise into the air, 
but kept her eyes shut. She hoped he would never put her down. She 
like being in his arms.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Striker::
> 
> Striker smiles as Spears wraps her hands around his neck. He looks 
at her 
> face as she rests her head on his shoulder, activating his jetpack 
as he 
> hears her words. He didn't want to panic her, so he wouldn't fly 
too high, 
> but it was easier to fly a femm-bot than to walk with her in his 
arms.
> 
> "I won't fly too high," he says to her as his feet leave the 
ground, going up 
> about 5 feet.
